	$LF
]p
[p 
	[a class=intlink href=/Users/Profile/Mothrayas 
		"Mothrayas
	]a
	": The movie rules on completion now have clarified that a game with some kind of ending can be published upon reaching that ending, even if the game is otherwise still an endless game. As such, taking into account good audience response, accepting for Moons.
	$LF
